    "Name": "Crucible",
    "Details": "The Crucible is designed to inflict the largest amount of damage in the fastest amount of time, to achieve this it carries a Gauss Rifle in each arm and side torso together with 8 tons of ammunition. Though the twelve double heat sinks are more than enough for the Gauss Rifles, the additional heat sinks allow the Crucible pilot to ignore heat from plasma weapons and Inferno rounds. A Micro Pulse Laser is also fitted for anti-infantry operations. Fifteen tons of standard armor covers the chassis. To free room and weight for this equipment the Crucible uses an 300-rated XL Engine and Endo Steel chassis, as a result the Crucible can reach 54 km/h max speed and has 90 meter jump range.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.24</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
